    <item>
      <title>随着日本股市接近历史新高，日元看跌头寸增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/cautious-funds-boost-yen-shorts-as-japan-stocks-near-record-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本股市上涨至历史新高之际，资产管理公司将日元看跌头寸增加至一年多以来的最高水平，这表明投资者对货币风险仍持谨慎态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/cautious-funds-boost-yen-shorts-as-japan-stocks-near-record-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 04:19:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰富瑞 (Jefferies) 停止覆盖 Paytm，直至监管问题缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/jefferies-stops-coverage-on-paytm-until-regulatory-issues-ease</link>
      <description><![CDATA[杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 成为第一家放弃对 Paytm 运营商 One 97 Communications Ltd. 进行报道的大型外国券商，直到围绕这家苦苦挣扎的印度金融科技巨头的消息“稳定下来”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-19/jefferies-stops-coverage-on-paytm-until-regulatory-issues-ease</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Feb 2024 03:16:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于对需求的担忧挥之不去，油价从三周高点下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-19</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对需求前景的持续担忧抵消了中东持续的紧张局势，油价从三周以来的最高水平下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-18/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-feb-19</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Feb 2024 23:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
